data.title: Camilo Jose Cela Autograph
data.meta_description: Signed print (partly covered by the passepartout), 5,75 x 4 inch, signed in blue ballpoint ink "Camilo Jose Cela", attractively mounted (removable) for fine display with a photograph, shows Camilo Jose Cela in a close-up portrait (altogether 8,25 x 11,75 inch), in very fine condition.
data.text:
Signed print (partly covered by the passepartout), 5,75 x 4 inch, signed in blue ballpoint ink "Camilo Jose Cela", attractively mounted (removable) for fine display with a photograph, shows Camilo Jose Cela in a close-up portrait (altogether 8,25 x 11,75 inch), in very fine condition.

All of our pieces are sold with a Certificate of Authenticity. If a piece turns out to be wrong or if you do not like an autograph, you will get your money back for a lifetime.
